[http://www.readwriteweb.com/archives/yahoo_pipes_web_database.php Yahoo Pipes], focuses on remixing RSS feeds


[http://www.teqlo.com/ Teqlo], ocuses on letting people create mashups and widgets from web services and rss

[http://www.dapper.net/ Dapper], generic scraping service for any web site


